snippet.title: Tomb Raider -  GBC Longplay/Walkthrough #107 [4Kp60]
snippet.description:
Rating: 3.5/5

Positives: Graphics, Length, Animation is decent, Battery save, Cutscenes, Original Story

Negatives: I personally do not like the controls/feel, A lot of the puzzles are "find a switch", Audio, Overall the game just felt like a "chore" to play imo
